    "Content": "- **Local network access**: Required if your Immich server is on your local network\n\nIf you deny a permission, re-enable it in **System Settings → Privacy & Security**.\n\n## Contributing\n\nContributions are welcome! See [CONTRIBUTING.md](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/emerysilb/immibridge/main/CONTRIBUTING.md) for guidelines.\n\n## License\n\nMIT License - see [LICENSE](LICENSE) for details.\n",
